Stephanie Leonidas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephanie_Leonidas 0 Stephanie Leonidas (born 14 February 1984) is an English actress. She is perhaps best known for her roles as Helena in the fantasy film MirrorMask and as Irisa on the American science fiction television series, Defiance.
